Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must fight the towering foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kyodai na teki o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uteyo! Uteyo! Uteyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Bring to bear the rage of justice, Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Seigi no ikari o butsukero GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Rise once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru! Yomigaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The year is Universal Century 0079.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Luna II, also known as the second Moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is an asteroid that was brought out to obtain mineral resources in order to build the space colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to it is Side 7, the seventh cluster of space colonies, which had been in construction for two years
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.53,0:01:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,when the war between the Principality of Zeon and the Earth Federation Forces broke out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Four clusters of space colonies were decimated by the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and only a few space colonies within Side 6 still stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The space colonies which declared themselves the Principality of Zeon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,are located furthest from the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There, the Zeon leader, Gihren Zabi, calls for an attack against the weakened Earth Federation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.99,0:02:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,suggesting that he is the one who will save all of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cucuruz Doan's Island
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Core Fighter, Amuro! Do you copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gunperry has launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! I'll make contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.58,0:02:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll start the count from the docking searcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The objective is to cut it down by three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in, Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.21,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, we're okay for docking standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.81,0:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, activate the docking searcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser searcher synchronized!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.48,0:03:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Releasing Gundam Module B!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Core change!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for docking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nineteen seconds flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you do it four seconds faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the laser searcher isn't synchronizing fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright, we're receiving an emergency signal from the Federation Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:03:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,An Air Force S.O.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's it coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about the enemy's numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.74,0:04:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It couldn't possibly be an automatic signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll track its position!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Point 305!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Point 305?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better ask Amuro to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, separate the Core Fighter from the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.63,0:04:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to patrol Point 305 in the Core Fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, I'm separating the Gundam modules!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pick them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure ain't a pretty sight, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so, Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out, Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, it's too weird seeing the Gundam like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that island over there Point 305?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them to tell you what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! If you need anything, let us know immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. We're going to have to save these Federation guys, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy may still be close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound the alarm for level two battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Try not to move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why were these pilots tied to their seats alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And how come only the fighter's weapons were taken?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come here, soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get off this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I said stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're annoying! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's destroy that fighter, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Doan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This area shouldn't be completely occupied by the Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan, it's another soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He was pointing his pistol at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fight against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hand over your weapons peacefully, I won't hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand over my weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you can do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just go ahead and attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you because I don't want to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here where it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan, beat that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can beat my Zaku with that small fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be able to destroy you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I fire a missile at the right spot, you won't be able to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have to destroy the joints!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get him this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rollan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Doan and the children's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cucuruz Doan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.16,0:10:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the person who saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.11,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan is going to send you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But until your wounds heal, you can rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, where's my Core Fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like Doan said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan is at the farm out back with the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan, it's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.37,0:11:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you should be walking around, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to protect these children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, Zeon will find this place and attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I also need weapons to protect myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return my Core Fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I return it, you'll just attack us, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like you, deceiving children to get them to obey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fighting the Zeon invaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're insulting Doan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not deceiving us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him protecting our island?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're just going to be mean to Doan, then leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you manipulate them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always told you to steer clear of pointless quarrels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to look for my Core Fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he moved it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.72,0:12:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan, he won't find his fighter, will he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he'll find it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more stubborn than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You were following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem to realize how beautiful the sunset is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In battle, there's no time to think about beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let your guard down, you'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is not as bad as you make him out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Doan is pretty good at deceiving children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't jump to conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's so great, then why did he hide my Core Fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand how those children feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think those children follow him around this island because he deceived them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then why is Doan trying to take care of those children?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to find out, ask him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan is looking forward to talking with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that once you shed that immaturity of yours, you'll become a good soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like he's on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, we'll call off the search until tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's worried about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He at least should have contacted us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Amuro we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he has a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.27,0:14:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's a stupid thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Zaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still no sign of the Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.45,0:15:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,About the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't leave him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,His main force should be nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't see things our way, it could be troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:16:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to get away from this life of constantly looking over my shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.33,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and leave our island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like both of us had trouble sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll continue the search!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Unidentified aircraft approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming in pretty fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it headed toward us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's headed toward Point 305.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's send out Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base will launch as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and leave our island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Zaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rollan, where are the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan, give me back my Core Fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Our house!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that Zaku aiming at?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, he's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That one Zaku is on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Please launch the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dock with it in mid-air!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back to the ship and convert here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Omur! Prepare for an emergency conversion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've got the skill to do it in mid-air.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This Zaku is all that's left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Let me handle this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't have any weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you mobile suit martial arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch and learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But Doan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.51,0:19:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll continue to fight as long as the children are watching!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan! Beat that Zaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan will win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not exactly sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid, I'll tell you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.79,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who killed these children's parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All because of a stray round from my gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Zeon ordered me to kill the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the children and ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I will protect these children with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.00,0:20:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,kill the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan, you were really cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're our hero, Doan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't stop chasing me until I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.15,0:21:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm alive, these children will face danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not because you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's your scent of battle that attracts pursuers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Scent of battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.05,0:21:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me wipe that scent away from you, Cucuruz Doan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.99,0:22:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.36,0:22:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you do something so terrible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.34,0:22:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna beat him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.21,0:22:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be mad at that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doan, he sunk it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What that boy did is a very good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.30,0:22:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rollan, I think he's a fine young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gallop and Gouf appear in the desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting to know Char's whereabouts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...Sayla disobeys orders\Nand launches into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Her reckless actions\Nput the Gundam in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Amuro's rescue attempt succeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla's Agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla's Agony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.64,0:23:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:54.91,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:59.91,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:10.13,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:15.05,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:19.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:25.06,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:29.65,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:39.95,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
